== 风暴 ==

=== 第一号热带风暴 ===
5月29日，从[[纽约|纽约]]出发，计划在[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]东侧靠岸的船只“黄金法则号”（{{lang|en|Golden Rule}}）在行进至[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]西部时遭遇热带风暴产生的狂风暴雨，最终于5月30日沉没。船员之后飘流到附近岛屿，经过十天的等待终于获两艘美国船只救援。<ref name="year" />估计风暴的风速达到每小时95公里，但具体移动路线已不可考<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160810161332/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | date = 2016-07-06 | accessdate = 2016-09-08 | archivedate = 2016-08-10 }}</ref>。

=== 第二号热带风暴 ===
据《[[时代花絮报|新奥尔良时报]]》（{{lang|en|''New Orleans Times''}}）报导，6月30日，[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[布朗斯维尔_(得克萨斯州)|布朗斯维尔]]附近出现热带风暴<ref name="year" />，估计其风速为每小时95公里。但是，考虑到气旋经过的地区人烟稀少，观测数据不足，这些数据可能不够准确。<ref name="usts">{{cite web |author=Hurricane Research Division |year=2011 |title=Continental United States Tropical Storms: 1851–1930, 1983–2010 |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2016-09-09 |archivedate=2016-03-04 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304202716/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/uststorms1851-1930%261983-2010-may11.html |url=http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/uststorms1851-1930&1983-2010-may11.html }}</ref>风暴的具体移动路线同样无从考证<ref name="HURDAT" />。

